  <fr:mainmatter>
  <fr:tree show-metadata="false"><fr:frontmatter><fr:authors /><fr:date><fr:year>2026</fr:year><fr:month>3</fr:month><fr:day>24</fr:day></fr:date><fr:title text="Execution Units">Execution Units</fr:title></fr:frontmatter><fr:mainmatter>
<html:p><html:strong>TensorCores</html:strong></html:p>
<html:figure><html:img width="100%" src="/bafkrmiawkeiezeyt4tj2lm6rbqjnjsupiyppuiwgebgqwrq2yx22ui2bcq.png" />
<html:figcaption>The TensorCore architecture</html:figcaption></html:figure>
<html:ul><html:li><html:em>Vector register file</html:em> each register is 8x128 vector registers with 8 horizontal lanes and 128 vertical lanes. There are typically 64 of these registers.</html:li></html:ul>
<html:p><html:strong>The Vector Processing Unit</html:strong></html:p>
<html:ul><html:li>2D SIMD execution, where each of 1024 <html:em>sites</html:em> execute same program in lockstep.</html:li>
  <html:li>Each site contains 4 ALUs, enabling 4096 FLOPs.</html:li>
  <html:li>Fed a 8x128 VREG in one cycle.</html:li></html:ul>
<html:p><html:strong>Matrix Multiplication Unit</html:strong> (MXU).</html:p>
<html:ul><html:li>256x256 totaling 65,536 <html:em>multiply accumulate</html:em> units i.e. each unit can multiply and add in one cycle.</html:li>
  
    <fr:tree show-metadata="false" toc="false"><fr:frontmatter><fr:authors /><fr:date><fr:year>2026</fr:year><fr:month>3</fr:month><fr:day>24</fr:day></fr:date><fr:taxon>Remark</fr:taxon></fr:frontmatter><fr:mainmatter>
  Can only do 256x256 matrix multiplication, so the order is 
  <html:ol><html:li>Tiling the matrix to load from HBM to VMEM</html:li>
    <html:li>Compiler tiles from VMEM to 256x256 tiles to load into MXU.</html:li></html:ol>
  </fr:mainmatter></fr:tree></html:ul>
<html:figure><html:img width="30%" src="/bafkrmickrnx5efnigkyxbpwks6lud2meikoqmsfy2llhy6lvb2y2bccpia.png" />
<html:figcaption>Note the input are offset so that the result from the first column can be accumulated int the second column. Can compute matmul in <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[2n - 1]]></fr:tex> cycles.</html:figcaption></html:figure>
</fr:mainmatter></fr:tree>
</fr:mainmatter>
